# dompdf writes per-font generated artifacts into the font dir on first use:
# - <family>_<style>_<hash>.ttf  (copy of the source TTF)
# - <family>_<style>_<hash>.ufm  (Adobe Font Metrics)
# - installed-fonts.json         (family -> file mapping)
# These are runtime artifacts; only the source TTFs and README.md are tracked.
*_*.ttf
*_*.ufm
installed-fonts.json
